title: 101 Healthy Vegan Desserts by Daniel Nadav
description:
101 original, easy and delicious healthy vegan recipes from all over the world (Cakes, Muffins, Cookies and Ice creams).

After the dizzying success of the three previous bestsellers, Daniel NadavÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s third cookbook is mainly for people who are crazy about desserts and, on the other hand, want to maintain a healthy and harmonious vegan diet.
